data.description: WOW, 4 bedrooms, 3 FULL baths over 1500 sq ft ranch. Updated open floor plan, large kitchen with tons of counter space, all stainless steel appliances included, large flex space currently used as a dining room, living space with gas fireplace and direct access to the backyard. All 3 baths almost completely updated. Primary bedroom w/private bath. 2 additional nice sized bedrooms on entry level. Basement offers 4th bedroom with egress window, renovated bath with new shower, large rec space w/new flooring, laundry room and storage space too. Hardwood floors in most of entry level, Large backyard with shed, pool, and poured parking pad that could be used to build a 2 car garage. Additional updates to the home include, roof 2017, newer appliances, windows to name a few. Must see to appreciate the large open floor plan.  Pool can stay or removed.
